reviewText: I bought this mainly for part 2. Was filmed here where I live. The places iv been, a bunch of my friends are in it, and the places I've played with my band. Great story lines and with a vampire movie with Boobs?? Can't go wrong!!!
There really isn't a bad fullmoon movie if your a true fullmoon universe fan.

Decadent Evil is a borderline camp classic, followed by the not as popular sequel. I, Vampire is a garbage trilogy using outtakes from three full length features. It doesn't count. Consider this a 2 DVD set.

Guide: F-bomb, sex, nudity.
